Subject: [PATCHv2 08/59] x86/mm: Introduce helpers to read number,
 shift and mask of KeyIDs
Date: Wed, 31 Jul 2019 18:07:22 +0300
Message-Id: <20190731150813.26289-9-kirill.shutemov@linux.intel.com>
